text: Yelko Gómez (born March 9, 1989 in Chiriquí Province) is a Panamanian cyclist. He has been riding for Hyundai-Momi-Continental since 2015. In 2014 and 2015 he won the National Time Trial Championships. Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Cyclists Category:Panamanian sportspeople
